content:
I'm stuck on something silly. Have a pc connected over the network with input as attached, but there is no visual indication top-right or elsewhere that there is valid input.

Any ideas aout there?

@Håkan Svensson
image.png

The multiplexer are accepting each message - green, i.e not filtered.
The multiplexer don't check for position. Your sentences are OK. The GNSS receiver don't report any position but the sentences are valid. OCPN will though not have a valid position. At least not from the messages shown.
bild.png
